{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1700-02_127", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Nouveau Prix proposez par la Compagnie des Lanternistes de Toulouse]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", février 1700 [tome 2], p. 127-131."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mrs les Lanternistes de Toulouse donneront un Prix cette année, à leur ordinaire. Voicy ce qu’ils ont fait imprimer sur ce sujet."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "BOUTS RIMEZ"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Proposez par les Lanternistes,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[2]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[3]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour l’année"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": " 1700."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "On a lieu d’esperer que nos Bouts-rimez plairont beaucoup cette année. On a pris soin qu’ils eussent quelque rapport à la situation des choses presentes ; & comme il n’y a rien de plus agréable que la Paix, il estoit malaisé de ne pas l’avoir en veuë dans le choix qu’on a fait de ces Rimes. Elles sont toutes propres à inspirer de beaux sentimens pour la gloire du Roy, de ce grand Monarque qui nous a procuré cette Paix d’une maniere tout à fait heroïque. Le retour de l’innocence & des solides plaisirs, le rétablissement des beaux Arts & du Commerce, fournissent une matiere remplie de nouveaux agrémens. Que de merveilles à décrire ! Que de vertus à representer ! Est il de plus doux attrait, de plus charmante invitation pour les Muses ' C’est en travaillant sur un si noble sujet, qu’elles peuvent s’acquerir une réputation immortelle"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Olive."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Eclatans."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Temps."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Active."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Attentive."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Contens."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Titans."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Captive."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Saison."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Orizon."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Barriere."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Soutenir."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Carriere."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Avenir."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Sonnets doivent estre accompagnez d’une Priere en quatre Vers pour le Roy, & d’une Sentence. Les Auteurs mettront leur seing couvert & cacheté au bas de leurs Sonnets, ou dans une Lettre separée, le tout sous la même envelope, & rendu franc de port chez M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": " Seré, prés la Place de Roaïx à Toulouse, huit jours avant la Saint Jean. On avertit que les Sonnets qui seront en petits Vers, ou à rimes composées, ne pourront prétendre au Prix."}]}]}]}